description: This file is a configuration include file for MIPS architecture tuning options in a Yocto/OpenEmbedded build environment. It sets compiler flags, feature flags, and package suffixes tailored for different MIPS processors like 24Kc and 24KEc in both big-endian and little-endian variants.

methods.name: bb.utils.contains
methods.description: A utility method used to check if a specific value is contained within a build variable or list.
